<span id="freeTextContainer3078702836657629580">My favorite bits are the two pornographic novels-within-the-novel, Garvey Ulm&apos;s <i>Get With Child a Mandrake Root</i> and Kilgore Trout&apos;s <i>Venus on the Half-Shell</i>, both marvelously suggested by illustrative paragraphs. Philip José Farmer was tasteless enough actually to write the second book. I suppose we can at least be glad that he didn&apos;t get around to writing the first one as well.</span>
