      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/4076-god-bless-you-mr-rosewater-or-pearls-before-swine">Quotes from God Bless You, Mr...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
